[2] Jiangxi
Date: 14 Jun 2017
Source: FIC (Flu Information Centre/Flu in China) [edited]
http://www.flu.org.cn/en/news_detail?action=ql&uid=&pd=&newsId=19518


Jiangxi province reported one new human H7N9 AIV case from 5-11 Jun 2017, according to the HFPC of Jiangsu province. The patient was reported in Xuzhou city.

