[3] Guangxi
Date: 17 Jun 2017
Source: FIC (Flu Information Centre/Flu in China) [edited]
http://www.flu.org.cn/en/news_detail?action=ql&uid=&pd=&newsId=19525


During the period between 9-15 Jun 2017, the Guangxi Zhuang Autonomous Region reported one human H7N9 AIV case (55-year-old male) in Baise city.

The Guangxi Zhuang Autonomous Region has reported a total of 27 human H7N9 AIV cases (including 14 fatal, 13 discharged from hospital) since 2017.

